<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="41" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1530,2036]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,320,1850,1876]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Melichar" box="[330,523,1850,1876]" pageId="12" pageNumber="44" refString="Melichar, L. (1914) Monographie der Tropiduchinen (Homoptera). Verhandlungen des Naturforschenden Vereins in Brunn, 53, 1 - 145." type="journal article" year="1914">
Melichar (
<number box="[454,515,1850,1876]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41" value="1914.0">1914</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authority="Melichar, 1914" authorityName="Melichar" authorityYear="1914" box="[657,957,1850,1876]" class="Insecta" family="Tropiduchidae" genus="Sogana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stimulata">
<emphasis box="[657,766,1851,1876]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="41">stimulata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Melichar" box="[776,957,1850,1876]" pageId="12" pageNumber="44" refString="Melichar, L. (1914) Monographie der Tropiduchinen (Homoptera). Verhandlungen des Naturforschenden Vereins in Brunn, 53, 1 - 145." type="journal article" year="1914">
Melichar, 
<number box="[898,957,1850,1876]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41" value="1914.0">1914</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
based on one single male species from Mentawei Islands, 
<collectingCountry box="[372,490,1890,1916]" name="Indonesia" pageId="12" pageNumber="41">Indonesia</collectingCountry>
. We were not able to see any specimens of this species. This species is externally similar to 
<taxonomicName box="[271,467,1931,1956]" class="Insecta" family="Tropiduchidae" genus="Sogana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="robustocarina" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[271,467,1931,1956]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="41">S. robustocarina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[475,569,1930,1956]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[475,569,1930,1956]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
from Borneo (Kalabakan) but can be distinguished from the latter by the vertex with one black spot at apex, frons with 
<number box="[692,706,1970,1996]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41" value="5.0">5</number>
carmine transverse bands, fore wings without nebula apically, and vertex with the sublateral carinae distinctly curving outwards (see 
<bibRefCitation author="Melichar" box="[979,1161,2010,2036]" pageId="12" pageNumber="44" refString="Melichar, L. (1914) Monographie der Tropiduchinen (Homoptera). Verhandlungen des Naturforschenden Vereins in Brunn, 53, 1 - 145." type="journal article" year="1914">
Melichar, 
<number box="[1098,1161,2010,2036]" pageId="12" pageNumber="41" value="1914.0">1914</number>
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
